    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/45b504dce3fb14073608a698be13d1f8.avif?t=1772010353\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras_big/45b504dce3fb14073608a698be13d1f8.avif?t=1772010353 width=800 height=122 /></span>Pick your character and step into Amer’s world where the fights hit harder than your mom’s slipper and the drama feels like a family WhatsApp group gone wrong. No floppy animals or jelly bodies here, just families settling scores, uncles jumping in for no reason, and chaos that actually makes sense to us. Whether you're teaming up or turning on each           other like always, expect wild twists, loud laughs, and pure Arab-style madness in the party fighting game        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/7661d894c1cd25559100e767181221b2.poster.avif?t=1772010353\" width=700 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/7661d894c1cd25559100e767181221b2.webm?t=1772010353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/d41859e09110308f5c9a6ce09cad2cdb.poster.avif?t=1772010353\" width=700 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/d41859e09110308f5c9a6ce09cad2cdb.webm?t=1772010353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/713f2cbf4c53486e74bab2087a971062.avif?t=1772010353\" width=1006 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                     Grab, lift, and throw, it’s as simple as that, and somehow… it creates the most chaos  <br>        Our grab mechanic lets you pick up your friends, carry them around, and launch them straight off the map</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >         Every match becomes funnier, louder, and way more unpredictable the moment someone decides to start<br>                                                                      grabbing everyone in sight</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/1a3486c77d260ee04652be20c53082d7.poster.avif?t=1772010353\" width=700 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/1a3486c77d260ee04652be20c53082d7.webm?t=1772010353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/fb8db553b086d7bca77aca759b9b0a6d.avif?t=1772010353\" width=1006 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your characters don’t just fight they start talking, yelling, and throwing random voice lines in the middle of the  chaos Every match turns into a mix of reactions, roasting, and unexpected screams that make the whole round                                                                                         way funnier </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                    Turn up your volume and enjoy the madness</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/a859f585db238fa1171d2b190798b0a7.poster.avif?t=1772010353\" width=1170 height=482 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/a859f585db238fa1171d2b190798b0a7.webm?t=1772010353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/13f7feb957cd5b522059bc728ddc0d61.avif?t=1772010353\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras_big/13f7feb957cd5b522059bc728ddc0d61.avif?t=1772010353 width=800 height=171 /></span>                                                Get ready for the ultimate family fighting game! Choose</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > from a variety of exciting maps, each with its own unique theme and challenges, for an unforgettable experience filled                                          with fun, chaos, and friendly competition for everyone to enjoy.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/51a4f6ac6665ab25dad5bf09748e319e.poster.avif?t=1772010353\" width=700 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/51a4f6ac6665ab25dad5bf09748e319e.webm?t=1772010353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/a4f2bdb8d5827c41dfae0a4715993c22.avif?t=1772010353\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras_big/a4f2bdb8d5827c41dfae0a4715993c22.avif?t=1772010353 width=800 height=122 /></span>Forget those clumsy games where characters flop around like they don’t know what’s going on. Here you set the traps, catch people slipping, and make moves that actually matter. Outsmart the rest, sit back, and claim your win like it’s                                                                    just another family roast session.    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/2228bd3b5996a844c0a491fd1c82a484.poster.avif?t=1772010353\" width=700 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264920/extras/2228bd3b5996a844c0a491fd1c82a484.webm?t=1772010353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
